'''''Seminars in Cardiothoracic and Vascular Anesthesia''''' is a quarterly [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[medical journal]] that covers research in the field of [[anesthesiology]] applied to [[cardiology]]. The [[editor-in-chief]] is Nathaen Weitzel ([[University of Colorado]]). It was established in 1997 and is currently published by [[SAGE Publications]].

== Abstracting and indexing ==
''Seminars in Cardiothoracic and Vascular Anesthesia'' is abstracted and indexed in [[CINAHL]], [[EMBASE]], [[MEDLINE]], and [[Ovid]].

